learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-27T17:09:25.577Z",codex-agent,Ownership-safe non-owner mutations should remain split by intent (metadata-only vs dep-only) to prevent accidental lifecycle drift while still enabling audit workflows.
